Package starvationevasion.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PolicyCard
    PolicyCard is the structure that the Simulator maintains for each card in the deck.

    When a card is played it becomes a Policy for voting and implementation purposes.
    PolicyProvider
    The PolicyProvider interface is implemented by any class that provides policy cards to the simulator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardDeck
    The CardDeck class
    Constant
    This class contains all constant values used throughout the Starvation Evasion game.
    Policy
    Policy is the structure that the Server uses to tell the Simulator which policies have been enacted on the current game turn.

    The game client's might want to extend this class adding, for example, an image, a status (in deck, in hand, proposed, voting, enacted, rejected) and other data.
    PolicyManager
    The PolicyManager class is a service provider that aggregates and provides all of the available policy cards found in the VM's classpath.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EnumFood
    The game models the following 12 farm product categories.

    All farm products throughout the world used for food, animal feed and/or biofuel are modeled as belonging to one of the above 12 categories.

    Farm products not modeled include Lumber, Cotton, and Wool.
    EnumRegion
    Enumerates each of the geographic regions used in the game: both Player and non-Player regions.

    The ordinal of US regions are continuous and less than all non-Player world regions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PolicyManager.DuplicatePolicyException
